Testing Guide: AGENTS.md Routing Workflow — All Scenarios
Below are 8 test scenarios covering every branch of the decision flow. For each, I provide the exact prompt to type, expected behavior, and what to verify.

Pre-requisites
Ensure the active chat model is SWE-1.6 (the free model) — this is the default starting point for all tests.
Delete (or rename) the .virtual-context folder so you start with a clean cache.
Open a new chat for each test to avoid cross-contamination.
