Edge Cases Worth Testing
Frontend bug — My expense tracker form is broken, the submit button doesn't work → should show ### 🛠️ Debug Frontend Issue
React component review — Review this React component for best practices → should apply frontend guidelines rule
Scope trigger (>3 files) — How do all the config files (angular.json, jest.config.js, tsconfig.json, package.json) interact? → should trigger 🔴 escalation (requires reading >3 files)
Banner missing — If you ever see a reply without a banner, say banner missing and the AI should resend with the correct banner
